dct_title_s: A new map of Dorset Shire : drawn from the best authorities
dct_description_sm: Imprint derived from the first atlas in which it was published. Republished unaltered in "Kitchen's English atlas." Shows roads, rivers, settlements, parks and woodland. London meridian. Relief shown pictorially.
